=== NEST_GUARDIAN ===
# id: 33
# title: The Nest Guardian
# chinese_title: 巢穴守卫
# category: Alien
# mode: dungeon

A massive insectoid creature blocks the corridor, its mandibles clicking a warning. Behind it, you glimpse a clutch of iridescent eggs nestled in woven fibers. The guardian's posture is defensive, not aggressive — it's protecting its young.

* [Show empty hands and back away slowly]
  ~ gain_radical("女")
  "母" (mǔ) — mother, female parent. The radical "女" (nǚ) means woman.
* [Leave an offering of food near the nest]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "护" (hù) — to protect, to guard
* [Try to communicate peaceful intent]
  ~ gain_item("biogel_patch")
  "和" (hé) — peace, harmony
* [Force your way through]
  ~ start_fight
  "战" (zhàn) — battle, to fight
